 is of paramount importance in the field of biomechanics; in this\nperspective, Bayesian inference represents a promising approach. This study was\nfocused on the analysis of the knee meniscus as a paradigmatic example of human\nsoft tissue.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Dec 2021 18:47:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-28"}
