ce permutation models in dimensions greater than or\nequal to $2$ are also discussed. The order $\\log{n}$ mixing time upper bound\npertains to the two-parameter permutation model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Dec 2021 22:06:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-28"}
