 details, but needed another global\nscan for final confirmation in the case of non-prototypical shapes, possibly\ndue to the current limitations of electrovibration technology in displaying\ntactile stimuli to a user. We observed that it was highly difficult to follow\nthe edges of shapes and recognize shapes with more than five edges under\nelectrovibration when a single finger was used for exploration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Dec 2021 22:33:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-28"}
