icular cascades over the parallel cascades as PSP\napproaches the Sun is observed. A dominant 2D cascade and/or geometry over the\nslab component in slow solar wind turbulence in the largest MHD scales is\nobserved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Dec 2021 15:50:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 12 Mar 2022 17:50:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 16 May 2022 15:12:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-18"}
